          "instruction": "Faster speed → less time. Inverse proportion.",
          "working": "60 × 5 = 100 × t → t = 300/100 = 3 hours",
          "result": "3 hours",
          "voice_text": "Speed and time are inversely proportional. 60 times 5 equals 100 times t. t equals 3 hours."
        }
